trans-unit.source: You can handle the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.ProgressChanged?displayProperty=fullName> event to implement a navigation progress bar for the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser> control similar to the one in Internet Explorer.
trans-unit.target: 你可以处理<xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.ProgressChanged?displayProperty=fullName>事件以实现的导航进度条<xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser>控件类似于 Internet Explorer 中的一个。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.ProgressChanged?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserProgressChangedEventArgs.CurrentProgress%2A> property to determine the number of bytes that have been downloaded successfully.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserProgressChangedEventArgs.CurrentProgress%2A>属性以确定已成功下载的字节数。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserProgressChangedEventArgs.CurrentProgress%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserProgressChangedEventArgs.MaximumProgress%2A> property to determine the number of bytes available for downloading.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserProgressChangedEventArgs.MaximumProgress%2A>属性来确定可供下载的字节数。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserProgressChangedEventArgs.MaximumProgress%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserProgressChangedEventArgs"></xref> class.
The number of bytes that are loaded already.
The total number of bytes to be loaded.
Gets the number of bytes that have been downloaded.
You can use this property to display the current navigation progress in a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar> control.
trans-unit.target: 你可以使用此属性来显示在当前的导航进度<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar>控件。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserProgressChangedEventArgs.MaximumProgress%2A> property to determine the total number of bytes available for downloading.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserProgressChangedEventArgs.MaximumProgress%2A>属性来确定总可供下载的字节数。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserProgressChangedEventArgs.MaximumProgress%2A>

trans-unit.source: The number of bytes that have been loaded or -1 to indicate that the download has completed.
trans-unit.target: -1 以指示下载已完成或已加载的字节数。

trans-unit.source: Gets the total number of bytes in the document being loaded.
trans-unit.target: 获取正在加载的文档中的总字节数。

trans-unit.source: You can use this property to display the current navigation progress in a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar> control.
trans-unit.target: 你可以使用此属性来显示在当前的导航进度<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar>控件。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserProgressChangedEventArgs.CurrentProgress%2A> property to determine the number of bytes that have been downloaded successfully.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserProgressChangedEventArgs.CurrentProgress%2A>属性以确定已成功下载的字节数。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserProgressChangedEventArgs.CurrentProgress%2A>

trans-unit.source: The total number of bytes to be loaded.
